Bihar B.Ed & Shiksha Shashtri Common Entrance Test CET Exam Answer Key 2022

Short Information : Lalit Narayan Mithila University, LNMU Darbhanga has released the Bihar B.Ed. Common Entrance Test (CET-BED)-2022 (B.Ed. & Shiksha Shastri) For All Universities of Bihar Running B.Ed. Course notification. Those Candidate Are Enrolled with Admission Test Can Download the Answer Key. For admission eligibility, age limit, college list, syllabus, university list, exam center and other information read the advertisement.

Lalit Narayan Mithila University, LNMU Darbhanga

Bihar B.Ed. Common Entrance Test (CET-BED)-2022 Answer Key

Short Details of Notification

WWW.SARKARIRESULT.COM

Important Dates

  • Application Begin : 25/04/2022
  • Last Date for Apply Online : 17/05/2022
  • Pay Exam Fee Last Date : 17/05/2022
  • With Late Fees Last Date Registration: 28/05/2021

  • Exam Date CBT : 06/07/2022
  • Admit Card Available : 25/06/2022
  • Answer Key Available : 07/07/2022
  • Result Declared : Notified Soon

Application Fee

  • General / : 1000/-
  • EBC/BC/EWS/Women : 750/-
  • SC / ST : 500/-
  • Pay the Exam Fee Through Debit Card, Credit Card, Net Banking.

Bihar B.Ed & Shiksha Shastri Programme Admission Details 2022

Course Name

Bihar 2 Year BEd Admission Eligibility
  • Bachelor Degree in Education (B.Ed) 2 Year Course.
  • Shiksha Shastri Programme
  • Bachelor Degree with Minimum 50% Marks in Any Recognized University in India.
  • For BE / B.Tech Candidates 55% Marks Required.
  • More Details Read the Notification.

Bihar B.Ed Common Entrance Test Exam District Details 2022

  • Patna, Gaya, Chapra, Ara, Bhagalpur, Darbhanga, Hajipur, Munger, Madhepura, Muzaffarpur & Purnea

  • Maulana Mazharul Haque Arabic and Persian University, Patna B.Ed College List 2022.
  • Munger University, Munger B.Ed College List 2022.
  • Patliputra University, Patna B.Ed College List 2022.
  • Purnea University, Purnea B.Ed College List 2022.
  • Tilka Manjhi Bhagalpur University, Bhagalpur B.Ed College List 2022.
  • Veer Kunwar Singh University, Ara B.Ed College List 2022.

How to Fill Bihar B.Ed & Shiksha Shastri Programme Online Form 2022

  • Lalit Narayan Mithila University, Kameshwaranagar, Darbhanga Released Notification for Combined B.Ed Entrance Test CET B.Ed 2022, Candidate Can Apply Start from 25/04/2022.
  • Candidate Read the Notification Before Apply the Admission Application Form in CET BEd Bihar Admission 2022.
  • Kindly Check and Collect the All Document - Eligibility, ID Proof, Address Details, Basic Details.
  • Kindly Ready Scan Document Related to Recruitment Form - Photo, Sign, ID Proof, Etc.
  • Before Submit the Application Form Must Check the Preview and All Column Carefully.
  • If Candidate Required to Paying the Application Fee Must Submit. If You have Not the Required Application Fees Your Form is Not Completed.
  • Take A Print Out of Final Submitted Form.
